                    <span>I have been waiting for this one for a long long time!!!!Besides Capone himself, my biggest passion has been the St. Valentine's Day Massacre.I finally got my wish bigtime and to make it even better,the one and only Helmer is on the case.I couldn't ask for more(perhaps Mattix)on this book to make it perfect.I just was fascinated by the new info and intricate details involved in what was supposedly an easy hit as reported by crime writers in history.Helmer knows his stuff along with Bilek they pull off a wonderful job in a book that i highly recommend!!!!</span>
                  
              
